notified, had been dead several days, Pacheco said. On the van's
windshield were parking tickets dating back to Tuesday.
   Lt. Charles Owen said an internal inquiry of methods and
procedures would be conducted.
   ``Again, the meter maids are not commissioned police officers,''
Owen said. ``They are civilians and that too will be considered.
Outside of being a trained observer, we don't really expect them to
make any type of investigations.''
